name: CDPANDA
description: CDPANDA is a community-driven meme token built on the base blockchain that combines humour, culture, vibes, fun and the love of memes. It celebrates the playful spirit of crypto builder culture powered by an active and loyal community of panda, and builder enthusiasts. No roadmap, no utility just a lovable panda skateboarding, surfing and vibing onchain. CDPANDA is all about spreading joy, building friendships and growing together on base.
